Local Modifications:
This is a heavily pruned copy of the source repository, containing only the
license file and the contents of the stdlib/public/Cxx subdirectory.
Added OWNERS, README.chromium, README.md.
Ported build rules from CMake to GN, with modifications to use Chromium's
libc++, and added the 'Chromium' prefix to module names to disambiguate them
from system modules.
